description: In the residence of Duvall a murder takes place, then a second ... and Inspector Ginko finds out that the person in charge of all the intrigue is Diabolik. But under what guise hides the great criminal?
name: L'impiccato

description: Diabolik needs some men to rob a bank. He recruits from the criminal underworld. It's a dangerous game to make a pact with six scoundrels ready for anything. But it is no less risky for that group of criminals to enter an alliance with the King of Terror.
name: Trappola Infernale

description: The House of Crime: The Minister of Justice, Frederick Duncan, chats with his wife and friends. The discuss Diabolik, who seems to have disappeared from the public eye. "Make no mistake," said the minister, "That murderer leaves time between one shot and the next, but then reappears bloodier than before!".
name: La Casa Del Delitto

description: Vittorio Pascal is an upright official of the Embassy, ​​living a slow paced life until the day a someone breaks into his home and blackmails him. Vittorio begins a nightmare of smuggling.
name: La Donna Decapitata

description: A ton of gold is in a steel case, fixed to the boxcar of a train, the transport organized by Inspector Ginko. His fear is that the gold will be stolen by Diabolik.
name: Lotta Disperata

description: Professor Philip Dumont and his wife Susan do not have a happy marriage. The couple fight and make empty threats about the insurance payoff if one of them were to die. This sets the perfect opportunity for Diabolik to capitalize on the couples animosity.
name: Delitto Perfetto

description: A disturbing message is published in a newspaper, among classified ads. Inspector Ginko and Diabolik will find themselves on the same side
name: Gidielli di Sangue

description: Diabolik and Inspector Ginko are in search of an alleged murderess obviously for different reasons.
name: Il morto che retorna

description: Alone, without shelter, without wealth and without any help, Diabolik is really cornered.
name: Ginko all attaco!
Having a Whale of a Time!

description:
The book opens with Eva bound and gagged to a chair, in the background a door, a light and the dark shadow of the King of Terror, Diabolik.

A flashback introduces the band of gangsters in the story. A gang that has a sordid history with Diabolik discover his identity. They kidnap Eva.
name: Il Rapimento di Eva

description:
The small kingdom of Beglait was restless: Diabolik has stolen the crown jewels. Inspector Ginko wants to face his greatest enemy, despite a thousand diplomatic difficulties ... but a strong and courageous woman helps him: Altea Duchess of Vallenberg.

This story introduces Altea.
name: Il Grande Ricatto

description: Altea Vallenberg and Inspector Ginko stay in a mountain resort. Diabolik is preparing something.
name: Il Pugnale Cinese

description: Strange things happen in Clerville: an old inmate is busted out, a castle which houses a museum is set on fire. Perhaps Diabolik who is weaving the fabric to complete a colossal blow?
name: L'Assassino dai 1.000 Volti

description: The director of a bank, Moltier Luigi, personally follows the transfer of a tremendous amount of money. Suddenly his bodyguards die and all the money disappears. Who is the distinguished man with the monocle?
name: Lo Sguardo che Uccide!

description: Count Cardie organized a treasure hunt in his castle: the goal is to find the ancient golden armor, hidden hundreds of years earlierjust a game, but the night a murder takes place, the first in a long, dramatic
name: Il castello della morte

description: Lex's ring soldiers have made plans that don't involve being his henchmen, or his fall guys. But as usual, he's one step ahead of everyone else—except Superman. We hope.
name: Chapter Twelve
